\section{Overview}

Our plan is
\begin{enumerate}
\item Rewrite Source Verse (\Cref{fig:source-verse-expr}) to Small Source Verse (\Cref{fig:small-source-verse}).
  Small Source Verse is simply a proper subset of Source Verse.
\item Desugar Small Source Verse into Big Core Verse (\Cref{fig:desugar-expr1}).
\item Simplify Big Core Verse into Core Verse (the ICFP 23 paper).
\end{enumerate}

% ----------------------------------------------------------------
\section{Source Verse}

\Cref{fig:source-verse-expr} gives the syntax of Source Verse.

\Cref{fig:sv-to-sv-1} and \Cref{fig:sv-to-sv-2} rewrite Source Version into simpler
Source Verse, ready for \Cref{fig:desugar-expr1}.


\begin{figure}
$$
